DOOMED HORIZON SOFTWARE - ordering program

Interactive program for ordering products from DOOMED HORIZON
SOFTWARE, a new Irish-based company founded by Noel O'Donnell
who produce quality software for the Amiga and are totally
dedicated to the Amiga's survival.




